    "To construct binary and discrete adjacency matrices, DosCond [54] and KiDD [30] model each pair of nodes as an independent Bernoulli variable.",
    "Then, the Gumbel-Max reparametrization trick [93] is utilized to address the non-differentiability challenges in the optimization procedure.",
    "Considering the diversity of optimization strategies and GC criteria, it is crucial to understand the characteristics ofTABLE IV: The accuracy (%) comparison between GC methods under different compression rates.",
